Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.79,0:00:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear big bro,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.68,0:00:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally delivered it. Sorry for taking so long. 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.06,0:00:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The sunflowers have been growing even taller than us, so I'm sure they'd be easy to find from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.06,0:00:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What skies are you flying about right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.52,0:00:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Even now, she's at the sunflower landmark...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:52.02,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fade(2500,2500)\pos(640,560)\fsp3\fs120\bord3\blur5\clip(0,0,150,720)\t(0,2600,\clip(0,0,1280,720))\3c&HFFFFFF&}Your Sky is Sorrowful
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.35,0:00:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear resident of the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.10,0:01:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Take good care of this letter, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.60,0:01:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter how many years have passed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.27,0:01:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This is proof that I'd lived, to her
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.18,0:01:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The ticket I showed you was one-way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.18,0:01:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and you congratulated me with skinny cheeks
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.27,0:01:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I hate honor, it's of secondary importance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.72,0:01:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So long
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.22,0:01:30.93,Default2,,0,0,0,,In the blue sky, I think of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.93,0:01:34.56,Default2,,0,0,0,,as I'm mistaken for a silver arrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.56,0:01:38.18,Default2,,0,0,0,,Your sky is sorrowful
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.18,0:01:41.81,Default2,,0,0,0,,The clouds swim, my first love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear my beloved,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.35,0:01:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,forgive me with this letter, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.89,0:01:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go home no matter how many years pass
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.56,0:01:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not crying, are you? I'm worried
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.56,0:02:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,As we watched the sunflowers in tedium,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.35,0:02:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,they bloomed in a line with a smile
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.64,0:02:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, home and social status are things of secondary importance
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.18,0:02:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I fell into love for the first time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.60,0:02:20.77,Default2,,0,0,0,,In the sunset, I think of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.22,0:02:24.47,Default2,,0,0,0,,singing praises of silver arrows
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.89,0:02:28.60,Default2,,0,0,0,,Your sea is sorrowful,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.60,0:02:31.89,Default2,,0,0,0,,the water's surface being dyed in the crimson of love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.18,0:02:35.77,Default3,,0,0,0,,An important-seeming letter
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.77,0:02:39.39,Default3,,0,0,0,,from a slightly dirty box,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.39,0:02:43.06,Default3,,0,0,0,,after many decades pass,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.06,0:02:46.64,Default3,,0,0,0,,finally reaches you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.22,0:03:04.89,Default3,,0,0,0,,I think of you today, too
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.89,0:03:08.52,Default3,,0,0,0,,Among sunflowers, a flower garden
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.52,0:03:11.81,Default3,,0,0,0,,While viewing this scenery,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.81,0:03:15.72,Default3,,0,0,0,,could you please smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:19.39,Default2,,0,0,0,,In the blue sky, I think of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.39,0:03:23.02,Default2,,0,0,0,,as I'm mistaken for a silver arrow
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.02,0:03:26.64,Default2,,0,0,0,,Your sky is sorrowful
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:29.97,Default2,,0,0,0,,Together with that, I think of my last love
